1:21:02.308 --> 1:21:03.932
Denny...

1:21:04.143 --> 1:21:06.143
Denny...

1:21:06.145 --> 1:21:08.279
Look at me.

1:21:09.181 --> 1:21:11.757
You don't have to do this.

1:21:12.026 --> 1:21:13.041
